-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Hurts_2B_Human&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: Technical and composing\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<link rel=\"mw-deduplicated-inline-style\" href=\"mw-data:TemplateStyles:r998391716\"/><div class=\"div-col\" style=\"column-width: 30em;\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Pink_(singer)\" title=\"Pink (singer)\">Pink</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; vocals, background vocals <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(tracks 2, 9)</span>, executive production, production <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(tracks 11, 13)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Wrabel\" title=\"Wrabel\">Wrabel</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; featured vocals, production <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 5)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Khalid_(singer)\" title=\"Khalid (singer)\">Khalid</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; featured vocals <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 6)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Chris_Stapleton\" title=\"Chris Stapleton\">Chris Stapleton</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; featured vocals <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 11)</span></li>\n<li>Jorden Odegard&#160;&#8211;&#32; all instruments (except guitar) <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 1)</span>, keyboards, strings, programming <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 6)</span>, production <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(tracks 1, 6)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Dan_Reynolds_(singer)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dan Reynolds (singer)\">Dan Reynolds</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; guitar, additional production <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 1)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Shellback_(record_producer)\" title=\"Shellback (record producer)\">Shellback</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; background vocals, keyboards, guitars, bass, drums, production, programming <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(track 2)</span></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Max_Martin\" title=\"Max Martin\">Max Martin</a>&#160;&#8211;&#32; keyboards, production, p